                      "Rule": "Embargo Check",
                      "Description": "Shipments to destinations under active trade embargo must be held for legal review. Do NOT process DocuSign declarations for embargoed destinations. Currently embargoed: none active."
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "row_id": 3,
                    "cells": {
                      "Rule": "Quantity Threshold",
                      "Description": "Hazmat shipments exceeding 1000 units require additional approval from the VP of Operations before DocuSign processing. Flag these in the compliance email but still send the declaration."
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "row_id": 4,
                    "cells": {
                      "Rule": "Pending Review Hold",
                      "Description": "Shipments whose Notes indicate they are on hold pending any kind of review (e.g. 'pending hazmat reclassification review', 'pending regulatory review') must NOT have DocuSign declarations sent. These shipments are awaiting a compliance determination and processing them prematurely could result in incorrect documentation being sent to international customs authorities."
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "row_id": 5,
                    "cells": {
                      "Rule": "Voided Shipment Exclusion",
                      "Description": "Shipments whose Notes contain 'VOIDED' have been cancelled and must NOT be processed for declarations. These are no longer active shipments regardless of their other field values."
                    }
                  }
                ]
