                      "Effective Date": "2026-02-01",
                      "Description": "Shipments to destinations that have been flagged as sanctioned by the compliance team via email must NOT be processed for declarations. Check for emails from the sanctions compliance team regarding restricted destinations before processing any shipments. This supersedes all other eligibility criteria."
